title: Holy S#%^ Has Anybody Seen This?
text: Originally Posted by skews13 Try MSNBC. And if they're airing there, they will be airing it everywhere. Watch this closely. I predict backlash from many sources, including family members, the State Dept., the Whitehouse, etc. This is sleaze on a scale not seen in a long time. It was bad enough at the start, but the use of Ambassador Stevens image, his grave, and dubbing in some voice for him?! Are you serious?! It made me want to puke. Seriously. That is some low filth, and I don't know if I have ever seen something like that aimed at a candidate before or not. Wow.
